@areainarea x @ambush_official x @gentlemonster

node.text:
4,843 ACRES of RAINFOREST SAVED @moetchandon x @ambush_official collaboration donation made it possible. 🙏🏽💚🍃
 
As you remember, #moëtchandon pledged to donate a portion of profits from the sale of limited-edition Moët & Chandon x #AMBUSH bottles to the @worldlandtrust – an international conservation charity that protects threatened natural habitats – to help preserve the #Canandé Reserve in the Ecuadorian #Chocó Forest, a place as biodiverse as the Amazon rainforest but far more threatened. The remarkable donation has had a direct impact on stopping the deforestation of the Chocó, not just for the sake of its fragile species but also to combat one of the causes of climate change.
 
I want to take this moment to thank you Moët & Chandon, for making my idea come to life and for everyone who purchased the bottles. You guys' support has contributed to the impact of this noble amazing cause! 

Here's the video from the @WorldLandTrust bout this donation: 

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SfrGhur_rzc

𝗔𝗠𝗕𝗨𝗦𝗛 𝑼𝑵𝑰𝑽𝑬𝑹𝑺𝑬, a deep dive into the world of AMBUSH®️.As expansive as our mind, the Universe is made up of complex forms and energies that are in constant motion. In the same way, AMBUSH UNIVERSE shows the power of rhythm and flow for evolution.Through exploration, the stories on #AMBUSHUNIVERSE widen our perspective and show us what is beyond the observable. You won't just find more planets and stars and forms, you will eventually find every possible thing in us and what we can become.𝙀𝙣𝙩𝙚𝙧 𝙏𝙝𝙚 𝙑𝙤𝙞𝙙 on:🪐 www.ambushdesign.com'AMBLEM' by @mmparisdotcom3D visuals: @keigakeiga
Music: @akirawoodgrain

“이제 패션 디자이너는 벽이나 커튼 뒤에 숨지 않는다. 오디언스는 디자이너와 소통하길 원하기에 하나의 ‘퍼스널리티’가 되어야 한다. 그 균형은 물론 자신에게 맞도록 조절해야 한다.” #보그 9월호를 위해 만난 #앰부시(@ambush_official)의 크리에이티브 디렉터 (@yoon_ambush)는 요즘 시대의 디자이너를 이렇게 정의합니다. 그녀와 나눈 이야기와 한국 남자 모델 8명이 앰부시의 가을 컬렉션을 입고 밤거리를 달린 화보를 지금 보그닷컴(vogue.co.kr)에서 확인하세요.
